Apple also makes several other products that it categorizes as "Wearables, Home and Accessories".<ref>{{Cite web |last=Leswing |first=Kif |date=2020-01-28 |title=Apple's fastest-growing business segment, which includes AirPods and Watch, is now bigger than Mac |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/01/28/apple-wearables-home-and-accessories-segment-now-bigger-than-mac.html |access-date=2022-10-19 |website=CNBC |language=en}}</ref> These products include the [[Apple headphones|AirPods]] line of wireless headphones, [[Apple TV]] digital media players, [[Apple Watch]] smartwatches, [[Beats Electronics|Beats]] headphones and [[HomePod Mini]] smart speakers.

